{"arkId":"cl010103606","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010103606","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1615","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1615,"imprecision":"","text":"D\u00e9but du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Duc, Dominique","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7027","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ovale ; couvercle et fond du bo\u00eetier grav\u00e9s de grotesques, au milieu de rinceaux sont sym\u00e9triquement dispos\u00e9s une t\u00eate d\u0027angelot, des oiseaux, des lapins, des fleurs. Carrure reperc\u00e9e et grav\u00e9e de dauphins dans des rinceaux fleuris. Revers du couvercle orn\u00e9 d\u0027une couronne de lauriers entourant une devise et un tournesol. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains  et, sur un disque mobile, \u00e0 chiffres arabes pour le r\u00e9veil. Aiguille et index en acier. Pourtour du cadran grav\u00e9 de rinceaux, de fleurs, d\u0027oiseaux et d\u0027une t\u00eate de ch\u00e9rubin. Mouvement \u00e0 sonnerie muni d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 verge, d\u0027une fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet reperc\u00e9s, grav\u00e9s de rinceaux \u00e0 fleurs de fraisier. Barillet du ressort de la sonnerie similairement d\u00e9cor\u00e9. Timbre fix\u00e9 dans le fond.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; devise : NON INFERIORA SEQCOR inscrivant un tournesol dont la tige est flanqu\u00e9e de deux C entrelac\u00e9s surmont\u00e9s d\u0027un S barr\u00e9 \r ; Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Dominique Duc \/ A Loches","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7,2","displayDimension":"7,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"4,5","displayDimension":"4,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"3,2","displayDimension":"3,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"France du centre = centre de la France (Europe) (Loches)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"19\/06\/1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"}],"place":[{"value":"France du centre = centre de la France"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tom